PrecisAppointment of ROBERT ALAN HOWALD of Streetsville, Ontario, Acting Vice-President, Real Estate, Eastern Region, to act as President and Chief Executive Officer of Canada Lands Company Limited to hold office during pleasure, in the stead of Jim Lynes, who has resigned, until such time as a President and Chief Executive Officer is appointed.
